{"tid":2205711,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 南投怪味雞 配 涼拌茄子","createTime":"2020-09-17T04:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T08:12:21.000Z","uid":33359,"like":94,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"628a99c5849ba3f5abab77f1b74a4beec10b8fff","tid":2205711,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8J9oko1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8J9oko1.jpg&h=e3f595ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdtXpQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdtXpQK.jpg&h=45e49a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zA3AbvN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzA3AbvN.jpg&h=1330093e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mBtTHCu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmBtTHCu.jpg&h=d2a19c05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞肉應該係預先整好放入雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人叫就加汁出餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以是凍食的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個汁幾好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先係好強既蒜味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後一入口係甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再慢慢先有咸味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞肉肉質幾嫩無臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n涼拌茄子好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醬汁好正宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似返到台灣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落條支氣管好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f045c956d08313cb2e683ba91